end="10.452">it</span> <span begin="10.452" end="10.999">takes</span> <span begin="10.999" end="11.206">is</span> <span begin="11.206" end="11.617">that</span> <span begin="11.617" end="11.948">one</span> <span begin="11.948" end="12.185">look</span> <span begin="12.185" end="12.376">you</span> <span begin="12.376" end="12.792">do</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只需你的一个眼神</span></p><p begin="12.792" end="14.547" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="12.792" end="12.869">And</span> <span begin="12.869" end="13.145">I</span> <span begin="13.145" end="13.359">run</span> <span begin="13.359" end="13.765">right</span> <span begin="13.765" end="14.026">back</span> <span begin="14.026" end="14.249">to</span> <span begin="14.249" end="14.547">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我便飞奔回你身边</span></p><p begin="14.878" end="18.671" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="14.878" end="14.943">You</span> <span begin="14.943" end="15.358">crossed</span> <span begin="15.358" end="15.508">the</span> <span begin="15.508" end="16.036">line</span> <span begin="16.436" end="16.555">and</span> <span begin="16.555" end="16.863">it&apos;s</span> <span begin="16.863" end="17.255">time</span> <span begin="17.255" end="17.337">to</span> <span begin="17.337" end="17.707">say</span> <span begin="17.707" end="17.917" amll:obscene="true">&quot;F</span> <span begin="17.917" end="18.671">you&quot;</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你越过了底线 是时候说声“该死的”</span></p><p begin="19.835" end="22.019" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="19.835" end="20.182">What&apos;s</span> <span begin="20.182" end="20.371">the</span> <span begin="20.371" end="20.797">point</span> <span begin="20.797" end="20.991">in</span> <span begin="20.991" end="21.584">saying</span> <span begin="21.584" end="22.019">that</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">说那些又有什么意义</span></p><p begin="22.533" end="24.375" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="22.533" end="22.636">When</span> <span begin="22.636" end="22.929">you</span> <span begin="22.929" end="23.160">know</span> <span begin="23.160" end="23.549">how</span> <span begin="23.549" end="23.861">I&apos;ll</span> <span begin="23.861" end="24.375">react</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你明明知道我会作何反应</span></p><p begin="24.592" end="26.802" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="24.592" end="24.783">You</span> <span begin="24.783" end="24.997">think</span> <span begin="24.997" end="25.193">you</span> <span begin="25.193" end="25.647">can</span> <span begin="25.647" end="25.932">just</span> <span begin="25.932" end="26.209">take</span> <span begin="26.209" end="26.502">it</span> <span begin="26.502" end="26.802">back</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你以为一切还能收回</span></p><p begin="27.368" end="29.387" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="27.368" end="27.432">But</span> <span begin="27.432" end="27.798" amll:obscene="true">shit</span> <span begin="27.798" end="28.149">just</span> <span begin="28.149" end="28.443">don&apos;t</span> <span begin="28.443" end="28.752">work</span> <span begin="28.752" end="29.073">like</span> <span begin="29.073" end="29.387">that</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">可该死的 事情从不是那样</span></p><p begin="29.671" end="34.282" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="29.671" end="29.899">You&apos;re</span> <span begin="29.899" end="30.087">the</span> <span begin="30.087" end="30.585">drug</span> <span begin="30.585" end="30.747">that</span> <span begin="30.747" end="31.110">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="31.110" end="31.352">ad</span><span begin="31.352" end="31.644">dict</span><span begin="31.644" end="31.924">ed</span> <span begin="31.924" end="32.426">to</span> <span begin="32.426" end="32.737">and</span> <span begin="32.737" end="33.043">I</span> <span begin="33.043" end="33.346">want</span> <span begin="33.346" end="33.573">you</span> <span begin="33.573" end="33.973">so</span> <span begin="33.973" end="34.282">bad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你是让我上瘾的毒药 我渴望你到极致</span></p><p begin="34.584" end="38.161" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="34.584" end="34.887">Guess</span> <span begin="34.887" end="34.996">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="34.996" end="35.482">stuck</span> <span begin="36.098" end="36.348">with</span> <span begin="36.348" end="36.708">you</span> <span begin="37.227" end="37.388">and</span> <span begin="37.388" end="37.695">that&apos;s</span> <span begin="37.695" end="38.161">that</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我想我就是离不开你 就这样吧</span></p><p begin="39.095" end="43.936" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="39.095" end="39.504">&apos;Cause</span> <span begin="39.504" end="39.808">when</span> <span begin="39.808" end="40.068">it</span> <span begin="40.068" end="40.616">all</span> <span begin="40.616" end="41.297">falls</span> <span begin="41.297" end="41.933">down</span> <span begin="41.933" end="42.429">then</span> <span begin="42.429" end="42.595">what</span><span begin="42.595" end="43.936">ever</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">因为当一切崩塌 怎样都无所谓了</span></p><p begin="44.372" end="48.660" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="44.372" end="44.702">When</span> <span begin="44.702" end="44.991">it</span> <span begin="44.991" end="45.527">don&apos;t</span> <span begin="45.527" end="46.145">work</span> <span begin="46.145" end="46.654">out</span> <span begin="46.654" end="47.277">for</span> <span begin="47.277" end="47.426">the</span> <span begin="47.426" end="47.610">bet</span><span begin="47.610" end="48.660">ter</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">当事情无法好转</span></p><p begin="49.314" end="54.173" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="49.314" end="49.596">If</span> <span begin="49.596" end="49.883">it</span> <span begin="49.883" end="50.562">just</span> <span begin="50.562" end="51.088">ain&apos;t</span> <